==Tatar==
===Etymology===
Akin to Old English ''curd, crud'', German ''gort milch'' - fermented milk;
Anglo-Indian ''curd''. 

#Phonetic Roman spelling: ''curd'', ''cort''
#Phonetic Cyrillic spelling: ''корт'', ''курд'', ''курут''

===Noun===
'''curd'''
# a type of cheese.

